<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Inspire • Modern Quote Wall</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root{
      --bg:#050816;
      --card:#0d1328cc;
      --text:#e8ecff;
      --muted:#a9b4d0;
      --line:#ffffff1f;
      --accent:#7c5cff;
      --accent2:#00d4ff;
      --accent3:#22c55e;
      --shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.45);
      --radius: 20px;
    }

    *{box-sizing:border-box}
    html,body{height:100%}
    body{
      margin:0;
      font-family:Inter,system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,Arial,sans-serif;
      color:var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(1000px 500px at 10% -10%, #7c5cff33, transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(900px 500px at 100% 0%, #00d4ff2a, transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(700px 400px at 50% 100%, #22c55e1f, transparent 65%),
        var(--bg);
      overflow-x:hidden;
    }

    .noise{
      position:fixed; inset:0; pointer-events:none; opacity:.05;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(to right, #fff 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(to bottom, #fff 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 3px 3px;
      mix-blend-mode:soft-light;
    }

    .container{
      width:min(1060px, 92%);
      margin:42px auto;
    }

    .hero{
      display:flex;
      align-items:flex-end;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:16px;
      margin-bottom:22px;
    }

    .badge{
      display:inline-flex;
      gap:8px;
      align-items:center;
      padding:8px 12px;
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius:999px;
      background:#ffffff08;
      color:#cbd5ff;
      font-size:13px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    }

    h1{
      margin:10px 0 6px;
      font-size:clamp(1.8rem,4vw,3rem);
      line-height:1.08;
      letter-spacing:-.02em;
    }

    .sub{
      margin:0;
      color:var(--muted);
      max-width:620px;
      line-height:1.6;
    }

    .btn{
      text-decoration:none;
      color:white;
      font-weight:600;
      padding:12px 16px;
      border-radius:12px;
      border:1px solid #ffffff29;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c5cff, #00b8ff);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 28px #4b57ff66;
      transition:.25s ease;
      white-space:nowrap;
    }
    .btn:hover{ transform: translateY(-2px); filter:saturate(1.15); }

    .grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
      gap:14px;
    }

    .card{
      grid-column: span 6;
      position:relative;
      background:var(--card);
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius:var(--radius);
      padding:20px 18px 16px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      overflow:hidden;
      isolation:isolate;
    }

    .card::before{
      content:"";
      position:absolute;
      width:160px; height:160px;
      right:-45px; top:-45px;
      border-radius:50%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #ffffff28, transparent 70%);
      z-index:-1;
    }

    .card.big{ grid-column: span 12; padding:26px 22px; }

    .q{
      margin:0;
      font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.5vw, 1.15rem);
      line-height:1.65;
      color:#f4f7ff;
    }

    .author{
      margin-top:12px;
      font-size:.92rem;
      color:#bcd2ff;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:8px;
    }
    .dot{
      width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:99px;background:var(--accent2);
      box-shadow:0 0 12px var(--accent2);
    }

    .highlight{
      display:inline-block;
      padding:4px 10px;
      border-radius:999px;
      font-size:.76rem;
      font-weight:700;
      letter-spacing:.04em;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      color:#d8dcff;
      border:1px solid #ffffff33;
      background:#ffffff0d;
      margin-bottom:12px;
    }

    .footer{
      margin-top:16px;
      color:#95a3c5;
      font-size:.88rem;
      text-align:center;
    }

    @media (max-width: 860px){
      .card{ grid-column: span 12; }
      .hero{ flex-direction:column; align-items:flex-start; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="noise"></div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero">
      <div>
        <span class="badge">✨ Daily Mindset • Modern Edition</span>
        <h1>Inspire. Build. Repeat.</h1>
        <p class="sub">A clean modern quote wall for your Docker web page — motivating, readable, and professional.</p>
      </div>
      <a class="btn" href="#" onclick="location.reload()">Refresh Vibe</a>
    </div>

    <section class="grid">
      <article class="card big">
        <span class="highlight">Featured</span>
        <p class="q">“You do not rise to the level of your goals. You fall to the level of your systems.”</p>
        <div class="author"><span class="dot"></span> James Clear</div>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <p class="q">“Success is the sum of small efforts, repeated day in and day out.”</p>
        <div class="author"><span class="dot"></span> Robert Collier</div>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <p class="q">“It always seems impossible until it’s done.”</p>
        <div class="author"><span class="dot"></span> Nelson Mandela</div>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <p class="q">“Great things are done by a series of small things brought together.”</p>
        <div class="author"><span class="dot"></span> Vincent van Gogh</div>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <p class="q">“Don’t watch the clock; do what it does. Keep going.”</p>
        <div class="author"><span class="dot"></span> Sam Levenson</div>
      </article>
    </section>

    <p class="footer">Made with ❤️ by Harish • Served from Docker + Apache</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
